Class FrevoMain.KeywordCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.FrevoMain.KeywordCategory
  • Enclosing class:
    FrevoMain

    public static class FrevoMain.KeywordCategory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a container for a category used for sorting different components. It contains a list of String objects (keywords) and a corresponding image.
